        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "1 Thessalonians 4:1",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "), as they appealed to the Christian standing of the readers and their conscious relationship to Christ, Whose coming in glory they expected.",
        "children": []
      },
