            "text": "",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "The Apostle is “writing no new commandment;” he recalls to his readers’ remembrance what he had so often urged upon them (see note on ch. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "1 Thessalonians 1:5",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "). It is on one prominent subject of those well-remembered charges that he has now to dwell:—",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
