      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Commandments (παραγγελίας)",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Better, charges. Only four times in N.T. olxx. The verb παραγγέλλειν to command or charge is frequent, and is often used in Class of military orders. See Xen. Cyr. ii., 4, 2; Hdt. iii., 25. ",
        "children": []
      }
    ]
  }
